HEADWORD: Thamyn
<hw>Tha"myn</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>An Asiatic deer (<spn>Rucervus Eldi</spn>) resembling the swamp
deer; -- called also <altname>Eld's deer</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

